Package: LIPIDIFy
Type: Package
Title: Comprehensive Lipidomics Data Analysis with Interactive Visualization
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Fayrouz", "Hammal", email = "fayrouz.hammal@petermac.org", 
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-7612-4953"))
    )
Description: Provides a comprehensive toolkit for lipidomics data analysis,
    including data preprocessing, normalization, differential abundance analysis
    using limma and EdgeR, enrichment analysis, and extensive visualization
    capabilities. Features both an interactive Shiny interface for biologists
    and programmatic R functions for bioinformaticians. Supports flexible lipid
    classification schemes and custom enrichment sets.
